name: Aks Moe
Lore: 'Gran senator from Malastare. A skillful politician who demanded that a commission be sent to Naboo to investigate the alleged occupation there.',
Text: 'Agendas: ambition, blockade. While in a senate majority, your capital starships are each power +2, and your Force drains are +1 at each battleground system where you occupy a related site.',
